      "path": "CLAUDE.md",
      "content": "# Project conventions\n\n- Any new CSS custom property must be prefixed `--gp-` (e.g. `--gp-highlight`).\n- Keep the whole site in a single index.html file with inline CSS.\n- Use Title Case for new section headings.\n"
    },
    {
      "path": "index.html",
      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n  <title>Demo User</title>\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --bg: #09090b;\n      --surface: #131316;\n      --text: #ededf0;\n      --muted: #8b8b96;\n      --accent: #5eead4;\n      --accent-2: #a78bfa;\n      --border: #232329;\n    }\n\n    * {\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n      box-sizing: border-box;\n    }\n\n    html {\n      scroll-behavior: smooth;\n    }\n\n    ::selection {\n      background: rgba(94, 234, 212, 0.25);\n    }\n\n    body {\n      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n      background: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--text);\n      line-height: 1.6;\n      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n    }\n\n    .container {\n      max-width: 720px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      padding: 0 24px;\n    }\n\n    /* Header / hero */\n    header {\n      position: relative;\n      padding: 96px 0 64px;\n    }\n\n    header::before {\n      content: \"\";\n      position: absolute;\n      top: -160px;\n      left: -120px;\n      width: 480px;\n      height: 480px;\n      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(94, 234, 212, 0.08), transparent 70%);\n      pointer-events: none;\n    }\n\n    .avatar {\n      width: 88px;\n      height: 88px;\n      border-radius: 50%;\n      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      font-size: 32px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      color: var(--bg);\n      margin-bottom: 24px;\n      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(94, 234, 212, 0.25);\n    }\n\n    h1 {\n      font-size: 40px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      letter-spacing: -0.02em;\n      margin-bottom: 8px;\n    }\n\n    .tagline {\n      font-size: 20px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      margin-bottom: 24px;\n    }\n\n    .intro {\n      font-size: 17px;\n      color: var(--text);\n      max-width: 60ch;\n    }\n\n    /* Sections */\n    section {\n      padding: 40px 0;\n      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n    }\n\n    h2 {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      margin-bottom: 24px;\n    }\n\n    /* Work / projects */\n    .section-note {\n      font-size: 16px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      max-width: 60ch;\n    }\n\n    .section-note a {\n      color: var(--accent);\n      text-decoration: none;\n    }\n\n    .section-note a:hover {\n      text-decoration: underline;\n    }\n\n    /* Skills */\n    .skills {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));\n      gap: 16px;\n    }\n\n    .skill {\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 12px;\n      padding: 20px 24px;\n    }\n\n    .skill h3 {\n      font-size: 16px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      margin-bottom: 4px;\n    }\n\n    .skill p {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      color: var(--muted);\n    }\n\n    /* Testimonials */\n    .testimonial-card {\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 12px;\n      padding: 24px;\n      margin-bottom: 16px;\n    }\n\n    .testimonial-card:last-child {\n      margin-bottom: 0;\n    }\n\n    .testimonial-card blockquote {\n      font-size: 16px;\n      font-style: italic;\n      margin-bottom: 12px;\n    }\n\n    .testimonial-card cite {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      font-style: normal;\n      color: var(--muted);\n    }\n\n    /* Contact links */\n    .links {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n      gap: 12px;\n    }\n\n    .links a {\n      display: inline-block;\n      padding: 10px 18px;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 999px;\n      color: var(--text);\n      text-decoration: none;\n      font-size: 15px;\n      transition: border-color 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;\n    }\n\n    .links a:hover {\n      border-color: var(--accent);\n      color: var(--accent);\n    }\n\n    footer {\n      padding: 40px 0 64px;\n      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n      color: var(--muted);\n      font-size: 14px;\n    }\n\n    @media (max-width: 480px) {\n      header {\n        padding: 64px 0 48px;\n      }\n\n      h1 {\n        font-size: 32px;\n      }\n\n      .tagline {\n        font-size: 18px;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <header>\n      <div class=\"avatar\">AK</div>\n      <h1>Demo User</h1>\n      <p class=\"tagline\">Software engineer &amp; builder</p>\n      <p class=\"intro\">\n        Hi, I'm Demo User. I build software and enjoy turning ideas into simple,\n        well-crafted tools. This is my corner of the internet — a place for\n        what I'm working on and how to reach me.\n      </p>\n    </header>\n\n    <section>\n      <h2>What I'm working on</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-note\">\n        I'm always building something — new projects will land here soon.\n        In the meantime, you can find my work on\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a>.\n      </p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section>\n      <h2>Skills</h2>\n      <div class=\"skills\">\n        <div class=\"skill\">\n          <h3>Web Development</h3>\n          <p>Building responsive, accessible sites with modern HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"skill\">\n          <h3>Backend &amp; APIs</h3>\n          <p>Designing and shipping reliable services, from data models to deployment.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"skill\">\n          <h3>Developer Tooling</h3>\n          <p>Automating workflows and crafting small tools that make teams faster.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section>\n      <h2>Testimonials</h2>\n      <div class=\"testimonial-card\">\n        <blockquote>&ldquo;Demo User turned a vague idea into a working product in weeks. Clear communication, clean code, and no surprises.&rdquo;</blockquote>\n        <cite>&mdash; Jordan Lee, Product Manager</cite>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"testimonial-card\">\n        <blockquote>&ldquo;One of the most reliable engineers I've worked with. The tooling they built saved our team hours every single week.&rdquo;</blockquote>\n        <cite>&mdash; Sam Rivera, Engineering Lead</cite>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section>\n      <h2>Get in touch</h2>\n      <div class=\"links\">\n        <a href=\"mailto:<email>\">Email</a>\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a>\n        <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">LinkedIn</a>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n      &copy; 2026 Demo User\n    </footer>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
    },
